<br>
- More people than you think can understand what they mean. Number increasing every year.<br>
- All characters have lots of meanings and connotations. A small dictionary probably can't reveal all of them. Same with friends you meet occasionally.<br>
- Japanese and Chinese have lots of homonyms (i. e. different characters that sound identically when read). Therefore, the characters you use might give sense in written form, but might be homonymous with something completely silly when pronounced (in Chinese or Japanese).<br>
- The same characters are used in Chinese and Japanese (sometimes with slight variants). It can happen that a certain character (or combination) has an interesting meaning in Japanese, but if read as Chinese word is nonsense or even silly. Or the other way round.<br>
- The styling (or you could say &quot;font&quot;) of a character is also important. There are traditional, manga, transparent, artistic, antique styles, among others. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.showPrevMessage?topicID=703.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.showNextMessage?topicID=703.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=703.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.threadControl?topicID=703.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=703.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=703.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionav